<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">في:</span> زياد بن سعد بن ضميرة <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>• زيد بن طهمان.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">صوابه:</span> يزيد بن طهمان، يأتي <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٢٢٥٠]</span> <span class="c2">((٦)</span> ت س) زيد بن ظَبيان الكوفي.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">روى عن:</span> أبي ذر.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">وعنه:</span> ربعي بن خراش.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>روى له الترمذي،<span class="c5"> والنسائي حديثًا واحدًا:</span> <span class="c2">(ثلاثة يحبهم الله (٧)</span>) <span class="c2">(٨)</span>، الحديث.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
